Join your fellow Kentico experts, enthusiasts, or anyone who wants to learn about Kentico in downtown Milwaukee, WI on Thursday, February 29.
:::note Date: 2024/2/29
Time: 5:00-7:00 PM CST
Location: 219 N Milwaukee St, Milwaukee, WI 53202, 2nd floor. :::
Hear how the team from [Kentico partner Heartland Business Systems](https://www.kentico.com/partners/heartland-business-systems--llc) helped Minnesota's fourth-largest credit union relaunch its website in less than 3-months and prepared to use the new migration tool to get to Xperience by Kentico later this year. Discover how they managed a rebrand and online banking challenges.
Register for the event and see [all the details on Meetup.com](https://www.meetup.com/mkekug/events/299194766/) or the [LinkedIn post](https://www.linkedin.com/posts/simmonsmktg_spring-meetup-penrod-thu-feb-29-2024-activity-7163899764235776000-J_yW?utm_source=share&utm_medium=member_desktop)
If you would like to see a Kentico user group start in your area, [let us know](https://community.kentico.com/#gridsection-feedback).
